{
  "title": "Fragrant Italian Chicken Pilaf",
  "description": "A cultured and shattering Italian dish featuring coriander seeds, this monsoon Italian recipe is a no-onion-no-garlic-friendly option, made with fry-grind-rice-khao-khua.",
  "cuisine": "Italian",
